:—The comparatively small flowers of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Leme" authorityYear="2011" box="[796,1023,1583,1608]" class="Liliopsida" family="Bromeliaceae" genus="Vriesea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="minutiflora">
<emphasis box="[796,1023,1583,1608]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Vriesea minutiflora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
inspired its name.
</paragraph>
